name: Harley Rouda
speech: Mr. ROUDA. Mr. Speaker, I missed votes on Friday, December 18, 2020,  at the recommendation of my physician. Had I been present, I would have  voted as follows: Roll Call Vote No. 246 on Motion to Suspend the Rules  and Pass ", S. 979, ': YEA; and Roll Call Vote No. 247 on Motion to Suspend  the Rules and Pass ', H.J.
